    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_garden-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、もうどこにも行かないでね\nさぁ、早速ドーナツを買いに行こ！",
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "待て待て、ドーナツを買いに行くのは構わないが\n未来から来た芽衣だって？　どういうことだ？",
      "startTime": 11.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "だって『昨日』ドーナツ買いに行くって約束したのに\n急にいなくなっちゃうんだもん……",
      "startTime": 18.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、それがすっごく心残りだったんだ\n悲しくて我慢出来なくて、つい未来から来ちゃった",
      "startTime": 25.3501148724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日？　全然理解出来ないぞ？\n来ちゃったって……未来から？　どうやって？",
      "startTime": 34.1061451733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ、ごめんねー\nそれは禁則事項で話せないんだー",
      "startTime": 40.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "禁則事項って……\nさっき話してくれた未来人の話みたいだが……",
      "startTime": 47.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "それよりもとりあえず、ドーナツドーナツだよー！\nはやくダンシングするために買いに行こ！",
      "startTime": 55,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　でも未来の芽衣が連れてっちゃったら\n{user}さんはいなくなっちゃう？",
      "startTime": 62.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら支度をしに行った芽衣は\n結局お出掛け出来なくて心残りが生まれちゃう？",
      "startTime": 67.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "つまりそれってえーっと……んん？\nま、いっかー！　ドーナツドーナツー！",
      "startTime": 78.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（うーん、俺をからかっているのか？　）\n（いや、だが嘘をついているようには見えないが……）",
      "startTime": 86.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さーん、ダメだよー\n行っちゃダメだよー。芽衣と一緒に行かないでー……",
      "startTime": 93.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 85.10050919998946,
          "startTime": 90.9506552237
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、ちょっと待ってくれ\n今、芽衣について考えていて……",
      "startTime": 100.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣！？　あれ！？　芽衣だよな！？\nえっ、芽衣が二人いる！？",
      "startTime": 105.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "あれれ？　芽衣だ！\n芽衣も未来から来ちゃったの？",
      "startTime": 110.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよー！　芽衣と同じで\n禁則事項の禁則事項して禁則事項な感じで来ちゃった",
      "startTime": 115.2826501573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が二人いて、会話している……\nつ、疲れているのか、俺は。こんな幻を見るなんて……",
      "startTime": 123.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "幻なんかじゃないよー！\nちゃんと芽衣達は本物の芽衣だよ！",
      "startTime": 132.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　二人とも未来から来た芽衣！\n禁則事項だから詳しくは話せないけど",
      "startTime": 139.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく{user}さん！\n芽衣と一緒にドーナツ買いに行っちゃダメ！",
      "startTime": 145.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツ食べちゃうと、{user}さんだけ\nすっごく酷い食あたりになっちゃうから……",
      "startTime": 151.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（なぜ俺だけ食あたりに……いや、目の前の芽衣達は）\n（幻じゃなく本物……だとしたら本当に未来から……？）",
      "startTime": 160.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "でもでも待って、ドーナツ買いに行けないと\n芽衣、悲しくなっちゃうよー？",
      "startTime": 169.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "未来の未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "でもでもでもでも、食あたりになっちゃったら\nそれこそ芽衣、悲しくなっちゃうよー",
      "startTime": 175.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない、やっぱり俺、疲れているんだな……\nリビングに戻って水を飲んでくるよ……",
      "startTime": 183.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei018_1.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！　いってらっしゃーい！",
      "startTime": 186.9011599699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "待ってたよ……{user}さん！\n未来から芽衣が来たから、もう安心だよ！",
      "startTime": 195.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（くっ、困ったな、まさかリビングに戻ったら）\n（また新しい芽衣が待ち受けているとは……）",
      "startTime": 202.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……未来の未来の……未来の芽衣か？\n遠い未来からやって来てたりするのか？",
      "startTime": 212.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "遠い未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ、すっごーい！　よく分かったね！\nでもどうやって来たかっていうのは……",
      "startTime": 218.9333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "禁則事項で話せないんだろう？\nはぁ……混乱し過ぎて逆に冷静になってきたよ",
      "startTime": 225.3666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それで未来の俺に今度は何があったんだ？\nドーナツで食あたりの次は虫歯にでもなったのか？",
      "startTime": 234.1000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "遠い未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "虫歯どころか、もっと大変なことだよー！\n闇の世界にダンキングして極悪フィクサーになったの！",
      "startTime": 242.2333394368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_11_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "何があった、未来の俺！？\nダンキングするのはドーナツだけにしておけよ",
      "startTime": 248.7333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "遥か未来の芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
